'''焦磷酸铁'''是一种铁的[[焦磷酸盐|焦磷酸盐]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为Fe<sub>4</sub>(P<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。
==制备==
焦磷酸铁可由[[偏磷酸铁|Fe(PO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>]]和[[磷酸铁|FePO<sub>4</sub>]]按[[化学计量比|化学计量比]]1：3于氧气中在[[氧化铝|氧化铝]]坩埚里加热得到。起始原料可用[[硝酸铁|Fe(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>·9H<sub>2</sub>O]]和磷酸的反应制备。<ref>LK Elbouaanani, B Malaman, R Gerardin, ''et al''. Crystal Structure Refinement and Magnetic Properties of Fe<sub>4</sub>(P<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>)<sub>3</sub> Studied by Neutron Diffraction and Mössbauer Techniques. Journal of Solid State Chemistry, 2002. 163 (2): 412-420. doi:10.1006/jssc.2001.9415</ref>

复分解反应也能得到焦磷酸铁：<ref>L. Rossi ''et al''. [https://www.uu.nl/sites/default/files/colloidal_ironiii_pyrophosphate_particles.pdf Colloidal iron(III) pyrophosphate particles] {{Wayback|url=https://www.uu.nl/sites/default/files/colloidal_ironiii_pyrophosphate_particles.pdf |date=20170203064236 }}. ''Food Chemistry'', 2014. 151. 243–247. doi: 10.1016/j.foodchem.2013.11.050</ref>
: 3 Na<sub>4</sub>P<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>(aq) + 4 FeCl<sub>3</sub>(aq) → Fe<sub>4</sub>(P<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>)<sub>3</sub>(s) + 12 NaCl(aq)
==应用==
用作补铁剂。
